{
  "number": 80,
  "name": "Abasa",
  "arabicName": "سُورَةُ عَبَسَ",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "totalAyahs": 42,
  "translator": "Saheeh International",
  "edition": "en.sahih",
  "language": "English",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "The Prophet frowned and turned away",
      "ayah_number": 1,
      "verse_key": "80:1"
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Because there came to him the blind man, [interrupting].",
      "ayah_number": 2,
      "verse_key": "80:2"
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "But what would make you perceive, [O Muhammad], that perhaps he might be purified",
      "ayah_number": 3,
      "verse_key": "80:3"
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Or be reminded and the remembrance would benefit him?",
      "ayah_number": 4,
      "verse_key": "80:4"
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "As for he who thinks himself without need,",
      "ayah_number": 5,
      "verse_key": "80:5"
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "To him you give attention.",
      "ayah_number": 6,
      "verse_key": "80:6"
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "And not upon you [is any blame] if he will not be purified.",
      "ayah_number": 7,
      "verse_key": "80:7"
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "But as for he who came to you striving [for knowledge]",
      "ayah_number": 8,
      "verse_key": "80:8"
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "While he fears [Allah],",
      "ayah_number": 9,
      "verse_key": "80:9"
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "From him you are distracted.",
      "ayah_number": 10,
      "verse_key": "80:10"
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "No! Indeed, these verses are a reminder;",
      "ayah_number": 11,
      "verse_key": "80:11"
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "So whoever wills may remember it.",
      "ayah_number": 12,
      "verse_key": "80:12"
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "[It is recorded] in honored sheets,",
      "ayah_number": 13,
      "verse_key": "80:13"
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Exalted and purified,",
      "ayah_number": 14,
      "verse_key": "80:14"
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "[Carried] by the hands of messenger-angels,",
      "ayah_number": 15,
      "verse_key": "80:15"
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Noble and dutiful.",
      "ayah_number": 16,
      "verse_key": "80:16"
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "Cursed is man; how disbelieving is he.",
      "ayah_number": 17,
      "verse_key": "80:17"
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "From what substance did He create him?",
      "ayah_number": 18,
      "verse_key": "80:18"
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "From a sperm-drop He created him and destined for him;",
      "ayah_number": 19,
      "verse_key": "80:19"
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "Then He eased the way for him;",
      "ayah_number": 20,
      "verse_key": "80:20"
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "Then He causes his death and provides a grave for him.",
      "ayah_number": 21,
      "verse_key": "80:21"
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "Then when He wills, He will resurrect him.",
      "ayah_number": 22,
      "verse_key": "80:22"
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "No! Man has not yet accomplished what He commanded him.",
      "ayah_number": 23,
      "verse_key": "80:23"
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "Then let mankind look at his food -",
      "ayah_number": 24,
      "verse_key": "80:24"
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "How We poured down water in torrents,",
      "ayah_number": 25,
      "verse_key": "80:25"
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "Then We broke open the earth, splitting [it with sprouts],",
      "ayah_number": 26,
      "verse_key": "80:26"
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And caused to grow within it grain",
      "ayah_number": 27,
      "verse_key": "80:27"
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "And grapes and herbage",
      "ayah_number": 28,
      "verse_key": "80:28"
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And olive and palm trees",
      "ayah_number": 29,
      "verse_key": "80:29"
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And gardens of dense shrubbery",
      "ayah_number": 30,
      "verse_key": "80:30"
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "And fruit and grass -",
      "ayah_number": 31,
      "verse_key": "80:31"
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "[As] enjoyment for you and your grazing livestock.",
      "ayah_number": 32,
      "verse_key": "80:32"
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "But when there comes the Deafening Blast",
      "ayah_number": 33,
      "verse_key": "80:33"
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "On the Day a man will flee from his brother",
      "ayah_number": 34,
      "verse_key": "80:34"
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "And his mother and his father",
      "ayah_number": 35,
      "verse_key": "80:35"
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "And his wife and his children,",
      "ayah_number": 36,
      "verse_key": "80:36"
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "For every man, that Day, will be a matter adequate for him.",
      "ayah_number": 37,
      "verse_key": "80:37"
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "[Some] faces, that Day, will be bright -",
      "ayah_number": 38,
      "verse_key": "80:38"
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "Laughing, rejoicing at good news.",
      "ayah_number": 39,
      "verse_key": "80:39"
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "And [other] faces, that Day, will have upon them dust.",
      "ayah_number": 40,
      "verse_key": "80:40"
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "Blackness will cover them.",
      "ayah_number": 41,
      "verse_key": "80:41"
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "Those are the disbelievers, the wicked ones.",
      "ayah_number": 42,
      "verse_key": "80:42"
    }
  ]
}